# .fridayrules  ─ concise living doc (<50 lines)

# ─── Architecture ───────────────────────────────────────────────
Frontend: React 18 + TypeScript, built with Vite (/src)
Routing: React Router DOM (/src/pages)
Styling: TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui components
State/Data: Convex serverless functions (/convex)
Shared code: /shared (TS utilities used by FE + BE)

# ─── Testing Guidelines ─────────────────────────────────────────
• No tests yet.
• Preferred stack: Vitest + React-Testing-Library (fast, Vite-native).
  - Install: pnpm add -D vitest @testing-library/react jsdom happy-dom
  - Config: vite.config.ts → test section.
• Place tests in src/__tests__ or *.test.ts(x).
• Run all tests:     pnpm vitest
• Watch mode:        pnpm vitest --watch
• CI:                pnpm vitest --run --coverage

# ─── Linting / Formatting ───────────────────────────────────────
Tooling: Biome (eslint + prettier replacement)
Key commands:
  pnpm lint          # analyze code
  pnpm lint:fix      # auto-fix issues
  pnpm format        # apply formatting (biome format --write .)
  pnpm check         # lint + type-check + build
Pre-commit: Husky + lint-staged trigger "pnpm lint:fix" & "pnpm format"
CI: pnpm check:ci (biome ci .)

# ─── End ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
